msgstr "Now let's apply what we just learned by this word study to James 5:14 <emphasis>\"Is any among you sick? Let him call for the elders of the church; and let them pray over him, anointing him with oil in the name of the Lord.\"</emphasis> Is \"anointing\" spiritual or practical? Practical!"

#: index.docbook:77
